name: 23 Sedgeford Road
description: Completely carbon neutral terraced house following a retrofit solar, batteries and air source heat pump installation. Existing radiators, double glazing and roof / loft insulation.

name: Grow, Hackney
description: Repurposed out of a disused sausage factory, Grow was converted into a grassroots venue, community hub, bar and kitchen. This canalside venue celebrates it 10th anniversary this year, and is part of an ecosystem of artist studios & small independent businesses & working yard.
address: 98c Wallis Road, Main Yard, Hackney Wick, E9 5LN
